the house on the coast where he has been coming for every one of 
his 64 summers except once during world war ii 
he also promised to drive his speedboat slowly when in the 
channel in the kennebunk river to permit lobstermen to continue to 
work their traps in the cove next to his house and to try not to 
hold up traffic 
barbara and i want to be good neighbors he told a town rally 
when he visited last thanksgiving 
