overhaul in the us system according to the louis harris survey 
commissioned for health management quarterly 
given a description of the canadian and british systems 61 
percent of americans said they would prefer to adopt the program 
used by their neighbors to the north and 29 percent said they would 
opt to try the british system according to the poll 
