<TEXT>
moslems in yorkshire wrote the latest chapter in 
the worlds long history of bookburning when they used a cigarette 
lighter to set fire to a copy of salman rushdies the satanic 
verses 
the moslems who mostly emigrated from pakistan to work in the 
